'''GRB 080913'''是由[[雨燕卫星|雨燕卫星]]于2008年9月13日观测到的一个[[伽玛射线暴|伽玛射线暴]]，随后包括[[伽马射线暴光学和近红外探测器|伽马射线暴光学和近红外探测器]]和[[甚大望远镜|甚大望远镜]]在内地面天文台和仪器进行了进一步观测。它的距离为128亿[[光年|光年]]，[[紅移#膨脹的宇宙|红移值]]为6.7，这个伽玛射线暴直到2009年4月23日[[GRB_090423|GRB 090423]]发现之前都是距离地球最为遥远的伽玛射线暴<ref>{{cite web | title=Astronomical Artifact: Most Distant Object Yet Detected Carries Clues from Early Universe | url=http://www.scientificamerican.com/article.cfm?id=most-distant-grb | work=Scientific American, a division of Nature America | accessdate=2010-02-23 | archive-date=2012-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012103248/http://www.scientificamerican.com/article.cfm?id=most-distant-grb | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=The Farthest Thing Ever Seen | url=http://www.skyandtelescope.com/news/43700627.html | work=Sky Publishing, Sky & Telescope | accessdate=2010-02-23 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120914143629/http://www.skyandtelescope.com/news/43700627.html | archivedate=2012-09-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title=Most distant object in the universe spotted| url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn17035-most-distant-object-in-the-universe-spotted.html| work=News Scientist| accessdate=2010-02-23| archive-date=2015-05-31| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150531111957/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn17035-most-distant-object-in-the-universe-spotted.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Breaking News | url=http://www.solstation.com/x-objects/grb000131.htm | work=Sol Station: Gamma-Ray Bursts 000131 - 090423 | accessdate=2010-02-23 | archive-date=2018-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715071513/http://www.solstation.com/x-objects/grb000131.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title= More Observations of GRB 090423, the Most Distant Known Object in the Universe | url= http://www.universetoday.com/2009/10/28/more-observations-of-grb-090423-the-most-distant-known-object-in-the-universe/ | work= Universe Today | accessdate= 2010-02-23 | archive-date= 2009-11-03 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091103114544/http://www.universetoday.com/2009/10/28/more-observations-of-grb-090423-the-most-distant-known-object-in-the-universe/ | dead-url= no }}</ref>。这次恒星爆炸大约发生在[[宇宙大爆炸|宇宙大爆炸]]8.25亿年之后<ref name='NASA'>{{cite news | first=Robert | last=Garner | coauthors= | title=NASA's Swift Catches Farthest Ever Gamma-Ray Burst | date=2008-09-19 | publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] | url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/swift/bursts/farthest_grb.html | work= | pages= | accessdate=2008-11-03 | archive-date=2020-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705194602/https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/swift/bursts/farthest_grb.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

